{"tid":2106960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［殘體慎入］澳門 今起内地所有城市居民到訪澳門無需14天隔離","createTime":"2020-07-13T14:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T19:44:27.000Z","uid":135572,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"08423f24cad3bdb81ed2504d9e5e721a46e43428","tid":2106960,"uid":135572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"今起内地所有城市居民到访澳门无需14天隔离<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新闻<br />\n2020-07-13 19:35<br />\n原标题：今起内地所有城市居民到访澳门无需14天隔离<br />\n<br />\n澳门发布微信公号7月13日消息，<br />\n<br />\n应变协调中心表示，今天（13日）起，澳门将北京和湖北省从高发地区名单中剔除，换言，内地所有城市居民到访澳门不需作14天医学观察。<br />\n<br />\n这是评估了内地整体疫情变化，以及对澳门的风险情况后而作出政策上的调整。<br />\n<br />\n协调中心进一步指出，虽然现时澳门疫情相对缓和，但必须指出新冠肺炎属于比较隐匿的病毒，可能存在一些无症状感染的个案，一旦乘坐渡轮或飞机均会存有传播风险。<br />\n<br />\n此外，协调中心强调，为配合内地的&ldquo;应检尽检&rdquo;的政策，保障飞机及渡轮工作人员的安全，以及减低把病毒带到社区的风险，因此要求所有乘坐飞机及渡轮的士均需出示核酸检测阴性结果的证明。<br />\n<br />\n（原题为：《澳门7月13日疫情记者会消息》<br />\n<br />\n汁： <a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/2020-07-13/detail-iivhuipn2788204.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2F2020-07-13%2Fdetail-iivhuipn2788204.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=4ca842f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/2020-07-13/detail-iivhuipn2788204.d.html?from=wap</a>"},{"pid":"c8c395367b5abf1bd61699e1eee38b8a595b76a2","tid":2106960,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f93b6777e14d1fc415f32ece74815060f2de505","tid":2106960,"uid":331739,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:38:37.000Z","msg":"45病例都自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"